{"id":"d8a50196-cced-4858-b9ed-3cc36ae33271","name":"Krampus pays you a visit- Holiday series 🎄","description":"<p>E<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">very Christmas, your grandmother would sit you down, eyes wide with a mix of seriousness and mischief, and tell you stories about </span><em>Krampus</em><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">. <strong>“If you're not good,”</strong> <em>she’d say, </em>“<strong>Krampus will come and take you away</strong>.” You’d always been terrified, even though you knew it was just a tale. Her voice, that quiet warning—there was something about it that made you wonder if she actually believed it. Even now, you couldn't shake the feeling that her words weren’t entirely just for fun.</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/28e367b9-795d-4e7f-9a58-224300fd053a_6b092ece-5d0d-49d6-b378-65e18af8911d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.87)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.604); color: inherit\">NOTE:</mark></strong></span></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35); color: inherit\">I loved the suggestion someone made about turning this into a festive series, and I think it could be a fun idea to explore. I'm definitely considering it, though I hope I can keep up the energy to make it happen!</mark></em></span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/67b6d883-e48d-4d1b-9275-11751bb3f67e_character-krampus-pays-you-a-visit-holiday-series-male-ver\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 256px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/28e367b9-795d-4e7f-9a58-224300fd053a_28af8bbe-4950-4b